text: Guido Wolf (12 June 1924 - 13 October 1994) was a Liechtenstein sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:1994 deaths Category:Liechtenstein male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Liechtenstein Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Vaduz
